                                belonged since <date when-iso="1804">1804</date>, along with other young poets and scholars.</p>
                            <p xml:lang="fr">L'abréviation <foreign xml:lang="grc">τ τ π α.</foreign> signifie <foreign xml:lang="grc">τò τоυ πόλου
                                    αστρον</foreign> ("Pole Star") et était la marque de fabrique de la <orgName ref="#g0031" type="bi">Northern Star
                                    Alliance</orgName>, à laquelle <persName ref="#p0237" type="bi">Chamisso</persName> et <persName ref="#p0248"
